{"video_id": "HZXg0W7no-0", "title": "Daily Evening Bhagavatam Discourse | HH Stoka Krishna Swami | SB 1.13.17 | 1-10-2022", "speaker": "HH Stoka Krishna Swami", "youtube_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HZXg0W7no-0", "duration": 899, "segments": [{"start": 0.0, "end": 7.16, "text": " ओ मज्ञानति मिरांदिस्य ध्यानां जविषलाकया चक्षुरुन्मीरितं येना तस्वैं श्री गुरवेदमहा"}, {"start": 7.16, "end": 14.3, "text": " नमाओ विष्टु पादाया कृष्ण प्रेष्ठाय भूतले श्री मते भक्ति वेदांत स्वाभिन दिति नामिने"}, {"start": 14.3, "end": 22.16, "text": " नमस्ते सारस्वते देवे गौरवाणी प्रचारिने निर्विशेशा शुन्यवादी पास्चात्य देशतारिने"}, {"start": 22.16, "end": 30.020000000000003, "text": " जय श्री कृष्ण चैतन्या प्रभूरित्क्यानन्दा श्री अद्वरित गदाजरा श्री वासानी गौरवक्त वृद्धा"}, {"start": 30.02, "end": 36.78, "text": " हरे कृष्ण हरे कृष्ण कृष्ण कृष्ण हरे हरे हरे रामा हरे रामा रामा रामा हरे हरे"}, {"start": 36.78, "end": 48.2, "text": " ओम नमो बगवते वासु देवाया नारायणम नमस कृत्या नरम चेवन अरोप्तमम देवीम सरस्वतीम व्यासम ततो जयम उदी रयेत।"}, {"start": 48.2, "end": 55.32, "text": " In this session we will be discussing from the 17th verse of 13th chapter of the 1st canto of Srimad Bhagavatam."}, {"start": 60.02, "end": 73.02000000000001, "text": " अनेशु सक्तानाम् प्रमत्तानाम् तदीहया अत्यक्रावण अविध्यातः कालपरमदुस्तरहाँ"}, {"start": 73.02000000000001, "end": 87.48, "text": " The meaning of this verse is insurmountable eternal time imperceptibly overcomes those who are too much attached to family affairs and are always engrossed in their thought."}, {"start": 90.02, "end": 99.02, "text": " So this is Sotu Goswami narrating to the sages of Maimishananya."}, {"start": 99.02, "end": 116.02, "text": " The reality about the time being wasted by Dhritarashtra, even though he is very nicely taken care of by Yudhishthira,"}, {"start": 116.02, "end": 120.02, "text": " he is spending his last few days,"}, {"start": 120.02, "end": 127.02, "text": " without utilising it properly for eternal benefit."}, {"start": 127.02, "end": 130.01999999999998, "text": " So that is going to be explained on top of that."}, {"start": 130.01999999999998, "end": 136.01999999999998, "text": " And that is the statement made by Sotu Goswami."}, {"start": 136.01999999999998, "end": 140.01999999999998, "text": " What is that? Insurmountable eternal time."}, {"start": 140.01999999999998, "end": 142.01999999999998, "text": " Time is eternal."}, {"start": 142.01999999999998, "end": 148.01999999999998, "text": " But it is continuously passing, passing, passing, passing, passing."}, {"start": 148.01999999999998, "end": 150.01999999999998, "text": " And nobody can overcome it."}, {"start": 150.02, "end": 156.02, "text": " The effect of time, the influence of time, nobody can overcome it."}, {"start": 156.02, "end": 159.02, "text": " No materialist can overcome it."}, {"start": 159.02, "end": 165.02, "text": " So imperceptibly this time overtakes us."}, {"start": 165.02, "end": 172.02, "text": " And particularly those who are too much attached to family affairs"}, {"start": 172.02, "end": 178.02, "text": " and engrossed in thought of the family, its well-being,"}, {"start": 178.02, "end": 185.02, "text": " and children and the bonding of affection between the different family members,"}, {"start": 185.02, "end": 189.02, "text": " like that time just passes away."}, {"start": 189.02, "end": 196.02, "text": " And human form of life is wasted without any eternal benefit."}, {"start": 196.02, "end": 200.02, "text": " So that is going to be explained on top of that."}, {"start": 200.02, "end": 202.02, "text": " So Srila Prabhupada says,"}, {"start": 202.02, "end": 204.02, "text": " I am now happy."}, {"start": 204.02, "end": 206.02, "text": " I have everything in order."}, {"start": 206.02, "end": 208.02, "text": " My bank balance is quiet enough."}, {"start": 208.02, "end": 210.02, "text": " I can now give my children their first aid."}, {"start": 210.02, "end": 212.02, "text": " I am now successful."}, {"start": 212.02, "end": 215.02, "text": " The poor beggar sannyasis depend on God."}, {"start": 215.02, "end": 219.02, "text": " But they come to me for begging from me."}, {"start": 219.02, "end": 223.02, "text": " Therefore I am more than the Supreme Father."}, {"start": 223.02, "end": 225.02, "text": " The Prabhupada says,"}, {"start": 225.02, "end": 228.02, "text": " These are some of the thoughts which engross"}, {"start": 228.02, "end": 231.02, "text": " the insanely attached householder"}, {"start": 231.02, "end": 234.02, "text": " who is blind to the passing of eternal time."}, {"start": 234.02, "end": 237.02, "text": " What Suta Goswami stated,"}, {"start": 237.02, "end": 239.02, "text": " Srila Prabhupada explaining,"}, {"start": 239.02, "end": 242.02, "text": " by going into a little more detail,"}, {"start": 242.02, "end": 246.02, "text": " what is the kind of thinking of people who are spiritually ignorant,"}, {"start": 246.02, "end": 249.02, "text": " having got the evil form of life."}, {"start": 249.02, "end": 252.02, "text": " They are always after material achievements,"}, {"start": 252.02, "end": 253.02, "text": " material happiness,"}, {"start": 253.02, "end": 255.02, "text": " material relationships,"}, {"start": 255.02, "end": 257.02, "text": " material prosperity."}, {"start": 257.02, "end": 263.02, "text": " Almost to the extent that they completely neglect spiritual."}, {"start": 263.02, "end": 265.02, "text": " Life."}, {"start": 265.02, "end": 267.02, "text": " So what is their thinking?"}, {"start": 267.02, "end": 272.02, "text": " They are thinking that actually they are happy."}, {"start": 272.02, "end": 275.02, "text": " Because presently their health is good."}, {"start": 275.02, "end": 280.02, "text": " Presently everything is going on okay."}, {"start": 280.02, "end": 282.02, "text": " Materially everything is going on okay."}, {"start": 282.02, "end": 284.02, "text": " They have enough money."}, {"start": 284.02, "end": 286.02, "text": " They have nice children."}, {"start": 286.02, "end": 292.02, "text": " Or they have enough to give their children"}, {"start": 292.02, "end": 294.02, "text": " their children inheritance."}, {"start": 294.02, "end": 295.02, "text": " They have saved enough."}, {"start": 295.02, "end": 299.02, "text": " And they consider themselves successful"}, {"start": 299.02, "end": 301.02, "text": " because they successfully managed to"}, {"start": 301.02, "end": 306.02, "text": " get a good job or a business."}, {"start": 306.02, "end": 309.02, "text": " And they have earned enough money."}, {"start": 309.02, "end": 313.02, "text": " So they also consider"}, {"start": 313.02, "end": 316.02, "text": " the spiritual, especially the sannyasis"}, {"start": 316.02, "end": 318.02, "text": " more renounced."}, {"start": 318.02, "end": 320.02, "text": " And therefore they don't"}, {"start": 320.02, "end": 324.02, "text": " they don't have money with them."}, {"start": 324.02, "end": 326.02, "text": " So they are renounced."}, {"start": 326.02, "end": 328.02, "text": " And they depend upon Krishna."}, {"start": 328.02, "end": 331.02, "text": " And in all humility they go and beg"}, {"start": 331.02, "end": 333.02, "text": " from householders"}, {"start": 333.02, "end": 335.02, "text": " to get some"}, {"start": 335.02, "end": 337.02, "text": " bhiksha, some little food"}, {"start": 337.02, "end": 339.02, "text": " for their basic needs and sustenance."}, {"start": 339.02, "end": 342.02, "text": " So these householders who are"}, {"start": 342.02, "end": 344.02, "text": " foolish, medievalists"}, {"start": 344.02, "end": 346.02, "text": " and a very attached to family,"}, {"start": 346.02, "end": 348.02, "text": " they think these sannyasis,"}, {"start": 348.02, "end": 350.02, "text": " they are just beggars."}, {"start": 350.02, "end": 352.02, "text": " And they say they depend on God"}, {"start": 352.02, "end": 353.02, "text": " but actually they are depending on"}, {"start": 353.02, "end": 355.02, "text": " a person like me."}, {"start": 355.02, "end": 357.02, "text": " And if I give some"}, {"start": 357.02, "end": 359.02, "text": " some small donation"}, {"start": 359.02, "end": 361.02, "text": " then they can"}, {"start": 361.02, "end": 363.02, "text": " they can maintain themselves."}, {"start": 363.02, "end": 366.02, "text": " Otherwise not even that."}, {"start": 366.02, "end": 368.02, "text": " So this is the"}, {"start": 368.02, "end": 370.02, "text": " total misunderstanding"}, {"start": 370.02, "end": 372.02, "text": " of these"}, {"start": 372.02, "end": 374.02, "text": " so called"}, {"start": 374.02, "end": 378.02, "text": " successful people, materialistic people."}, {"start": 378.02, "end": 379.02, "text": " So Prabhupada explains,"}, {"start": 379.02, "end": 382.02, "text": " our duration of life is measured"}, {"start": 382.02, "end": 385.02, "text": " and no one is able to enhance it"}, {"start": 385.02, "end": 387.02, "text": " even by one second"}, {"start": 387.02, "end": 389.02, "text": " against the scheduled time"}, {"start": 389.02, "end": 392.02, "text": " ordained by the supreme will."}, {"start": 392.02, "end": 394.02, "text": " So we got a fixed duration"}, {"start": 394.02, "end": 396.02, "text": " of time in this body."}, {"start": 396.02, "end": 398.02, "text": " Such valuable time"}, {"start": 398.02, "end": 400.02, "text": " especially for the human being"}, {"start": 400.02, "end": 402.02, "text": " should be spent"}, {"start": 402.02, "end": 404.02, "text": " very carefully, cautiously."}, {"start": 404.02, "end": 406.02, "text": " Because"}, {"start": 406.02, "end": 408.02, "text": " even a second passed"}, {"start": 408.02, "end": 410.02, "text": " imperceptibly"}, {"start": 410.02, "end": 412.02, "text": " cannot be replaced"}, {"start": 412.02, "end": 414.02, "text": " in exchange for"}, {"start": 414.02, "end": 418.02, "text": " thousands and millions of gold coins"}, {"start": 418.02, "end": 421.02, "text": " amassed by hard labour."}, {"start": 422.02, "end": 424.02, "text": " Supposing I lose time,"}, {"start": 424.02, "end": 426.02, "text": " I cannot regain that lost time"}, {"start": 426.02, "end": 428.02, "text": " by any means."}, {"start": 428.02, "end": 431.02, "text": " It is lost forever."}, {"start": 431.02, "end": 432.02, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 432.02, "end": 435.02, "text": " why is Prabhupada telling this?"}, {"start": 435.02, "end": 437.02, "text": " Every second of human life is meant"}, {"start": 437.02, "end": 439.02, "text": " for making an ultimate solution"}, {"start": 439.02, "end": 441.02, "text": " to the problems of life."}, {"start": 441.02, "end": 444.02, "text": " The fundamental problems of life."}, {"start": 444.02, "end": 446.02, "text": " Which we cannot solve"}, {"start": 446.02, "end": 450.02, "text": " except by spiritual method."}, {"start": 450.02, "end": 452.02, "text": " If we don't make a solution"}, {"start": 452.02, "end": 454.02, "text": " then we have the opportunity"}, {"start": 454.02, "end": 455.02, "text": " for spiritual practice"}, {"start": 455.02, "end": 457.02, "text": " in the human form of life."}, {"start": 457.02, "end": 461.02, "text": " Then we simply are going to repeat"}, {"start": 461.02, "end": 464.02, "text": " the cycle of birth and death."}, {"start": 464.02, "end": 466.02, "text": " And when repeating the cycle of birth and death,"}, {"start": 466.02, "end": 468.02, "text": " we may"}, {"start": 468.02, "end": 470.02, "text": " take birth"}, {"start": 470.02, "end": 472.02, "text": " in lower species."}, {"start": 472.02, "end": 474.02, "text": " And in the lower species"}, {"start": 474.02, "end": 476.02, "text": " if we take birth,"}, {"start": 476.02, "end": 478.02, "text": " there is no opportunity"}, {"start": 478.02, "end": 480.02, "text": " for somebody in the lower species,"}, {"start": 480.02, "end": 482.02, "text": " a soul in the lower species,"}, {"start": 482.02, "end": 484.02, "text": " to inquire about spiritual life,"}, {"start": 484.02, "end": 487.02, "text": " to take up the practice"}, {"start": 487.02, "end": 490.02, "text": " of spiritual life in lower life forms."}, {"start": 490.02, "end": 492.02, "text": " It is not possible."}, {"start": 492.02, "end": 493.02, "text": " Generally."}, {"start": 493.02, "end": 494.02, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 494.02, "end": 496.02, "text": " they are losing the birth"}, {"start": 496.02000000000004, "end": 498.02000000000004, "text": " and death opportunity"}, {"start": 498.02000000000004, "end": 500.02000000000004, "text": " for eternal life full of bliss and knowledge"}, {"start": 500.02000000000004, "end": 503.02000000000004, "text": " by not practicing spiritual life."}, {"start": 503.02000000000004, "end": 504.02000000000004, "text": " They spend away"}, {"start": 504.02000000000004, "end": 505.02000000000004, "text": " all their time"}, {"start": 505.02000000000004, "end": 508.02000000000004, "text": " in material pursuits."}, {"start": 508.02000000000004, "end": 509.02000000000004, "text": " And time lost"}, {"start": 509.02000000000004, "end": 513.02, "text": " is lost forever."}, {"start": 513.02, "end": 514.02, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 514.02, "end": 516.02, "text": " the ignorant people,"}, {"start": 516.02, "end": 518.02, "text": " spiritually ignorant people,"}, {"start": 518.02, "end": 519.02, "text": " they don't understand"}, {"start": 519.02, "end": 520.02, "text": " a fundamental fact"}, {"start": 520.02, "end": 522.02, "text": " about this material body."}, {"start": 522.02, "end": 523.02, "text": " What is that?"}, {"start": 523.02, "end": 524.02, "text": " This material body"}, {"start": 524.02, "end": 525.02, "text": " subject to birth,"}, {"start": 525.02, "end": 526.02, "text": " death,"}, {"start": 526.02, "end": 527.02, "text": " disease,"}, {"start": 527.02, "end": 528.02, "text": " old age."}, {"start": 528.02, "end": 529.02, "text": " And"}, {"start": 529.02, "end": 532.02, "text": " these four fundamental"}, {"start": 532.02, "end": 533.02, "text": " problems"}, {"start": 533.02, "end": 534.02, "text": " in the"}, {"start": 534.02, "end": 536.02, "text": " material body"}, {"start": 536.02, "end": 537.02, "text": " are the cause of"}, {"start": 537.02, "end": 539.02, "text": " all sufferings"}, {"start": 539.02, "end": 541.02, "text": " of the living being."}, {"start": 541.02, "end": 542.02, "text": " Otherwise,"}, {"start": 542.02, "end": 544.02, "text": " the living being himself"}, {"start": 544.02, "end": 546.02, "text": " is eternal"}, {"start": 546.02, "end": 547.02, "text": " and never born,"}, {"start": 547.02, "end": 548.02, "text": " never dies,"}, {"start": 548.02, "end": 550.02, "text": " never has to face"}, {"start": 550.02, "end": 553.02, "text": " old age or"}, {"start": 553.02, "end": 554.02, "text": " disease"}, {"start": 554.02, "end": 557.02, "text": " in this spiritual body,"}, {"start": 557.02, "end": 560.02, "text": " in this spiritual form."}, {"start": 560.02, "end": 562.02, "text": " Never has to face."}, {"start": 562.02, "end": 563.02, "text": " So, foolish people"}, {"start": 563.02, "end": 565.02, "text": " forget this"}, {"start": 565.02, "end": 566.02, "text": " that I have got"}, {"start": 566.02, "end": 567.02, "text": " a material body."}, {"start": 567.02, "end": 568.02, "text": " It is simply"}, {"start": 568.02, "end": 569.02, "text": " the source of"}, {"start": 569.02, "end": 571.02, "text": " all miseries."}, {"start": 571.02, "end": 572.02, "text": " But I am not meant"}, {"start": 572.02, "end": 574.02, "text": " for this material body."}, {"start": 574.02, "end": 575.02, "text": " In my original position"}, {"start": 575.02, "end": 579.02, "text": " as a transcendentalist,"}, {"start": 579.02, "end": 581.02, "text": " I am entitled"}, {"start": 581.02, "end": 582.02, "text": " to eternal life"}, {"start": 582.02, "end": 584.02, "text": " full of bliss and knowledge."}, {"start": 584.02, "end": 585.02, "text": " Without any"}, {"start": 585.02, "end": 586.02, "text": " of the miseries,"}, {"start": 586.02, "end": 587.02, "text": " without birth"}, {"start": 587.02, "end": 588.02, "text": " or death"}, {"start": 588.02, "end": 589.02, "text": " or disease"}, {"start": 589.02, "end": 590.02, "text": " or old age"}, {"start": 590.02, "end": 591.02, "text": " or any"}, {"start": 591.02, "end": 592.02, "text": " of the miseries."}, {"start": 592.02, "end": 593.02, "text": " And"}, {"start": 593.02, "end": 594.02, "text": " even if some people"}, {"start": 594.02, "end": 595.02, "text": " take note"}, {"start": 595.02, "end": 596.02, "text": " of these problems,"}, {"start": 596.02, "end": 597.02, "text": " miseries which"}, {"start": 597.02, "end": 598.02, "text": " crop up"}, {"start": 598.02, "end": 599.02, "text": " from time to time,"}, {"start": 599.02, "end": 600.02, "text": " they"}, {"start": 600.02, "end": 601.02, "text": " do not know"}, {"start": 601.02, "end": 602.02, "text": " how to solve"}, {"start": 602.02, "end": 603.02, "text": " these miseries"}, {"start": 603.02, "end": 604.02, "text": " in such a way"}, {"start": 604.02, "end": 605.02, "text": " that"}, {"start": 605.02, "end": 606.02, "text": " we come out"}, {"start": 606.02, "end": 607.02, "text": " of the miseries"}, {"start": 607.02, "end": 608.02, "text": " entirely"}, {"start": 608.02, "end": 609.02, "text": " that"}, {"start": 609.02, "end": 610.02, "text": " they do not know."}, {"start": 610.02, "end": 611.02, "text": " They become"}, {"start": 611.02, "end": 612.02, "text": " engrossed"}, {"start": 612.02, "end": 613.02, "text": " in the"}, {"start": 613.02, "end": 614.02, "text": " temporary"}, {"start": 614.02, "end": 615.02, "text": " family affairs"}, {"start": 615.02, "end": 616.02, "text": " not knowing"}, {"start": 616.02, "end": 617.02, "text": " that they are"}, {"start": 617.02, "end": 618.02, "text": " losing valuable"}, {"start": 618.02, "end": 619.02, "text": " time in human"}, {"start": 619.02, "end": 620.02, "text": " form of life."}, {"start": 623.02, "end": 624.02, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 624.02, "end": 625.02, "text": " this is called"}, {"start": 625.02, "end": 626.02, "text": " illusion."}, {"start": 626.02, "end": 627.02, "text": " This is called"}, {"start": 627.02, "end": 628.02, "text": " illusion."}, {"start": 628.02, "end": 629.02, "text": " More."}, {"start": 631.02, "end": 633.02, "text": " Such illusion"}, {"start": 633.02, "end": 634.02, "text": " cannot"}, {"start": 634.02, "end": 635.02, "text": " affect"}, {"start": 635.02, "end": 636.02, "text": " a person"}, {"start": 637.02, "end": 638.02, "text": " who is"}, {"start": 638.02, "end": 639.02, "text": " engaged"}, {"start": 639.02, "end": 640.02, "text": " in pure"}, {"start": 640.02, "end": 641.02, "text": " devotional service."}, {"start": 641.02, "end": 642.02, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 642.02, "end": 643.02, "text": " Yudhishthira Maharaj"}, {"start": 643.02, "end": 644.02, "text": " and the"}, {"start": 644.02, "end": 645.02, "text": " Pandavas"}, {"start": 645.02, "end": 646.02, "text": " they were"}, {"start": 646.02, "end": 647.02, "text": " all engaged"}, {"start": 647.02, "end": 648.02, "text": " in service"}, {"start": 648.02, "end": 649.02, "text": " of Lord Krishna."}, {"start": 649.02, "end": 650.02, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 650.02, "end": 651.02, "text": " they had"}, {"start": 651.02, "end": 652.02, "text": " very little"}, {"start": 652.02, "end": 653.02, "text": " attraction"}, {"start": 653.02, "end": 654.02, "text": " for illusory"}, {"start": 654.02, "end": 655.02, "text": " happiness"}, {"start": 655.02, "end": 656.02, "text": " because"}, {"start": 656.02, "end": 657.02, "text": " they know"}, {"start": 657.02, "end": 658.02, "text": " what is the value"}, {"start": 658.02, "end": 659.02, "text": " of this"}, {"start": 659.02, "end": 660.02, "text": " illusory"}, {"start": 660.02, "end": 661.02, "text": " happiness."}, {"start": 661.02, "end": 662.02, "text": " You know,"}, {"start": 662.02, "end": 663.02, "text": " it is worthless."}, {"start": 663.02, "end": 664.02, "text": " And they also"}, {"start": 664.02, "end": 665.02, "text": " know they have"}, {"start": 665.02, "end": 666.02, "text": " to prepare"}, {"start": 666.02, "end": 667.02, "text": " for eternal life"}, {"start": 667.02, "end": 668.02, "text": " by practicing"}, {"start": 668.02, "end": 669.02, "text": " devotional service."}, {"start": 669.02, "end": 670.02, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 670.02, "end": 671.02, "text": " they were"}, {"start": 671.02, "end": 672.02, "text": " engaged in"}, {"start": 672.02, "end": 673.02, "text": " Krishna consciousness."}, {"start": 674.02, "end": 675.02, "text": " And therefore,"}, {"start": 675.02, "end": 676.02, "text": " they were always"}, {"start": 676.02, "end": 677.02, "text": " attracted to"}, {"start": 678.02, "end": 679.02, "text": " spiritual"}, {"start": 679.02, "end": 680.02, "text": " perfection,"}, {"start": 680.02, "end": 681.02, "text": " achieving"}, {"start": 681.02, "end": 682.02, "text": " spiritual"}, {"start": 682.02, "end": 683.02, "text": " perfection"}, {"start": 683.02, "end": 684.02, "text": " at the end"}, {"start": 684.02, "end": 685.02, "text": " of life."}, {"start": 685.02, "end": 686.02, "text": " By practicing"}, {"start": 686.02, "end": 687.02, "text": " spirituality"}, {"start": 687.02, "end": 688.02, "text": " now in"}, {"start": 688.02, "end": 689.02, "text": " the human form"}, {"start": 689.02, "end": 690.02, "text": " when we got"}, {"start": 690.02, "end": 691.02, "text": " an opportunity."}, {"start": 691.02, "end": 692.02, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 692.02, "end": 693.02, "text": " Maharaj"}, {"start": 693.02, "end": 694.02, "text": " Yudhishthira"}, {"start": 694.02, "end": 695.02, "text": " was always"}, {"start": 695.02, "end": 696.02, "text": " fixed in"}, {"start": 696.02, "end": 697.02, "text": " the service"}, {"start": 697.02, "end": 698.02, "text": " of Lord Mukunda"}, {"start": 698.02, "end": 699.02, "text": " or Krishna."}, {"start": 699.02, "end": 700.02, "text": " And therefore,"}, {"start": 700.02, "end": 701.02, "text": " there was"}, {"start": 701.02, "end": 702.02, "text": " no"}, {"start": 702.02, "end": 703.02, "text": " point"}, {"start": 703.02, "end": 704.02, "text": " in"}, {"start": 704.02, "end": 705.02, "text": " seeking"}, {"start": 705.02, "end": 706.02, "text": " the"}, {"start": 706.02, "end": 707.02, "text": " happiness"}, {"start": 707.02, "end": 708.02, "text": " of life"}, {"start": 708.02, "end": 709.02, "text": " as it was"}, {"start": 709.02, "end": 710.02, "text": " in the kingdom"}, {"start": 710.02, "end": 711.02, "text": " of heaven"}, {"start": 711.02, "end": 712.02, "text": " and"}, {"start": 712.02, "end": 713.02, "text": " what"}, {"start": 713.02, "end": 714.02, "text": " to speak"}, {"start": 714.02, "end": 715.02, "text": " of"}, {"start": 715.02, "end": 716.02, "text": " the"}, {"start": 716.02, "end": 717.02, "text": " happiness"}, {"start": 717.02, "end": 718.02, "text": " available"}, {"start": 718.02, "end": 719.02, "text": " on the"}, {"start": 719.02, "end": 720.02, "text": " earth"}, {"start": 720.02, "end": 721.02, "text": " because"}, {"start": 721.02, "end": 722.02, "text": " he knows"}, {"start": 722.02, "end": 723.02, "text": " all"}, {"start": 723.02, "end": 724.02, "text": " these are"}, {"start": 724.02, "end": 725.02, "text": " illusory"}, {"start": 725.02, "end": 726.02, "text": " all these"}, {"start": 726.02, "end": 727.02, "text": " are temporal."}, {"start": 727.02, "end": 728.02, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 728.02, "end": 729.02, "text": " therefore,"}, {"start": 729.02, "end": 737.02, "text": " happiness, being attached to family life, they do not realize that insurmountable"}, {"start": 737.02, "end": 744.02, "text": " eternal time is overtaking them and they are losing valuable time, wasting it in some material"}, {"start": 744.02, "end": 753.02, "text": " pursuits. So they don't realize this doesn't apply to Yudhishthira Maharaj, it doesn't apply"}, {"start": 753.02, "end": 762.02, "text": " to Pandavas, it doesn't apply to devotees, it applies to Dhritarashtra who was actually"}, {"start": 762.02, "end": 775.02, "text": " out of attachment for his body, for his wife, for the comforts, material comforts that"}, {"start": 775.02, "end": 783.02, "text": " Yudhishthira was offering as a courtesy. He was lost in that and he was completely lost"}, {"start": 783.02, "end": 795.02, "text": " in neglecting spiritual life. So this verse is applicable to Dhritarashtra and Vidura"}, {"start": 795.02, "end": 808.02, "text": " had come exactly to shake up Dhritarashtra out of the ignorance and to instruct him how"}, {"start": 808.02, "end": 811.02, "text": " he can save himself before that comes."}, {"start": 813.02, "end": 826.02, "text": " So Srila Prabhupada says that one who is factually learned, he knows that material happiness"}, {"start": 826.02, "end": 833.02, "text": " is not important, it's not worthwhile. There is something called Brahma Sukha or absolute"}, {"start": 833.02, "end": 842.02, "text": " happiness, spiritual happiness. That Brahma Sukha or spiritual happiness is eternal and"}, {"start": 842.02, "end": 855.02, "text": " it is always unconditionally experienced by those engaged in devotional service. So such"}, {"start": 855.02, "end": 862.02, "text": " devotees, they have no attraction for any material, including material happiness or material"}, {"start": 862.02, "end": 864.02, "text": " comforts."}, {"start": 864.02, "end": 870.02, "text": " So Maharaj Yudhishthira actually was a true devotee of Yudhishthira. He was a true devotee"}, {"start": 870.02, "end": 871.02, "text": " of Yudhishthira."}, {"start": 872.02, "end": 880.02, "text": " He was spiritual, enlightened, was spiritually alert. But Dhritarashtra was not. So it"}, {"start": 880.02, "end": 885.02, "text": " was actually for the sake of Dhritarashtra that Vidura had come to enlightened Dhritarashtra"}, {"start": 885.02, "end": 894.02, "text": " and that is why we will hear how Dhritarashtra strongly instructs Dhritarashtra to come out"}, {"start": 894.02, "end": 898.02, "text": " of this illusion. I will stop here. Thank you very much."}]}